name: liftedFrom
help:
Level from which parcel is lifted. 
   Supported types: [STRING [SURFACE|MEAN_LAYER|MOST_UNSTABLE] ] 
   Ex: --liftedFrom SURFACE

name: virtualTemperature
help:
Specify if the virtual temperature correction should be applied. 
   Supported types: [STRING [YES|NO] ] 
   Ex: --virtualTemperature YES
